        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 32. Habitat for Asydates species. A) Open, flat valley 43.5 km south of Wells, Elko Co., NV, habitat of A. shoshone collected from flowers of Chrysothamnus viscidiflorus and Ericameria nauseosa. Photograph taken 7 July 2018 by Adriean J. Mayor. B) Roadside talus 7.2 km south of Sweetwater Summit along Highway 338, Lyon Co., NV, habitat of A. washoe collected from flowers of Eriogonum microthecum. Photograph taken 7 September 2018 by Adriean J. Mayor." ;
